data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to make this captivating 3BD/2BA, 2 STORY HOUSE your home! It offers a TON of STORAGE SPACE inside and a WOODEN PRIVACY FENCE in the backyard. This stunning property offers a perfect blend of COMFORT, STYLE, and PRIVACY. Situated on ALMOST HALF AN ACRE, the property boasts a generous outdoor space perfect for RELAXATION and entertainment. Backyard already has a CONCRETE PAD ready to put a shed on or even additional entertainment space! And all of this can be found in a MATURE, QUIET neighborhood. Contact me now to schedule a private viewing and experience the charm and comfort of this beautiful gem!
